<node ID="98B9D7DD-E030-49A1-A705-220714CC2087" TEXT="If users can assign a single verb, or a single task to a block of your content, then that&#8217;s a successful design." COLOR="#36342E" POSITION="right" STYLE="fork"><edge COLOR="#FEE221" WIDTH="5" /><font NAME="HelveticaNeue" SIZE="21" /></node>
